,"wantsCollapsedNewlines":true,"primarySubtitle":"1.19.5","secondarySubtitle":"Thu Feb 12 2026 17:49:00 GMT+0000 (Coordinated Universal Time)"},{"$kind":"TitledParagraph","text":"rollback to 1.17.0","style":"detail","wantsCollapsedNewlines":true,"primarySubtitle":"1.19.1","secondarySubtitle":"Fri Dec 19 2025 16:16:43 GMT+0000 (Coordinated Universal Time)"},{"$kind":"TitledParagraph","text":"- UI compatibility improvements for MacOS 26\n- Branding updates\n- Various bug fixes and enhancements","style":"detail","wantsCollapsedNewlines":true,"primarySubtitle":"1.19.0","secondarySubtitle":"Thu Dec 11 2025 15:37:57 GMT+0000 (Coordinated Universal Time)"},{"$kind":"TitledParagraph","text":"- Providers can now enable usage reporting by setting the new `reporter` in the YAML access key\n- Fixed a crash when using WebSocket access keys\n- Various bug fixes and enhancements\n\nFor more information, check out: https://github.com/Jigsaw-Code/outline-apps/discussions/2616","style":"detail","wantsCollapsedNewlines":true,"primarySubtitle":"1.17.0","secondarySubtitle":"Wed Aug 27 2025 22:56:08 GMT+0000 (Coordinated Universal Time)"},{"$kind":"TitledParagraph","text":"- Introducing \"Dark Theme\": you can switch themes via the \"Appearance\" menu now\n- Fixed an issue that would sometimes show a \"failed to connect\" false alert\n- General bug fixes and improvements","style":"detail","wantsCollapsedNewlines":true,"primarySubtitle":"1.16.1","secondarySubtitle":"Thu Aug 14 2025 19:07:47 GMT+0000 (Coordinated Universal Time)"},{"$kind":"TitledParagraph","text":"- Improved connection stability during network changes\n- Added scrollable and copyable error details\n- New dedicated, moveable window experience\n- Bug fixes","style":"detail","wantsCollapsedNewlines":true,"primarySubtitle":"1.15.2","secondarySubtitle":"Fri May 23 2025 00:41:04 GMT+0000 (Coordinated Universal Time)"},{"$kind":"TitledParagraph","text":"- Bug fixes","style":"detail","wantsCollapsedNewlines":true,"primarySubtitle":"1.15.1","secondarySubtitle":"Mon Apr 14 2025 18:59:30 GMT+0000 (Coordinated Universal Time)"},{"$kind":"TitledParagraph","text":"This update adds two key features:\n- Advanced Config: Customizable connections support multiple protocols (including WebSockets), separate TCP/UDP ports, and more. Enables future enhancements and simplifies adding new protocols. Existing configurations are still supported.\n- WebSockets: Supports Shadowsocks-over-WebSockets, wrapping traffic in web traffic for improved circumvention. Helps bypass protocol allowlisting and IP blocking.","style":"detail","wantsCollapsedNewlines":true,"primarySubtitle":"1.15.0","secondarySubtitle":"Thu Feb 20 2025 18:09:25 GMT+0000 (Coordinated Universal Time)"},{"$kind":"TitledParagraph","text":"This is rolling back to an earlier version because of issues on older macOS devices with our previous release 1.14.0.","style":"detail","wantsCollapsedNewlines":true,"primarySubtitle":"1.14.1","secondarySubtitle":"Tue Dec 10 2024 18:42:09 GMT+0000 (Coordinated Universal Time)"},{"$kind":"TitledParagraph","text":"- Added support for Happy Eyeballs server connection. Your server domain can now resolve to multiple IPs, including IPv6, and the app will use the first IP with a successful TCP connection\n- Provided more detailed error messages when connect fails\n- The client properly configures the VPN profile to allow for switching via the system settings and automation. The profile will show the name of the selected server – for the ability to disconnect via this menu, disable auto connect\n- Redesigned UI components for better user interaction\n  - Expanded text box in “adding new access key” dialog\n- Updated options on support contact form\n- Disables TCP Keep-Alive to reduce battery consumption\n- Bug fixes","style":"detail","wantsCollapsedNewlines":true,"primarySubtitle":"1.14.0","secondarySubtitle":"Fri Nov 15 2024 01:12:30 GMT+0000 (Coordinated Universal Time)"},{"$kind":"TitledParagraph","text":"We’re pleased to announce the v1.13 version of the client, which comes with two new features:\n\nProviders using Dynamic Keys can now send custom errors! You can use these errors to communicate quota exceeded, key revocation or send contact information, among other things. Learn how (link to wiki section)\nWe’ve revamped the customer support form to be more helpful. The intent is to get end users answers to common questions quickly, reducing load on our support team so they can in turn respond faster.","style":"detail","wantsCollapsedNewlines":true,"primarySubtitle":"1.13.0","secondarySubtitle":"Mon Apr 22 2024 19:00:34 GMT+0000 (Coordinated Universal Time)"},{"$kind":"TitledParagraph","text":"Basic error details for VPN connection issue debugging.\nFix popover click behavior.","style":"detail","wantsCollapsedNewlines":true,"primarySubtitle":"1.12.1","secondarySubtitle":"Thu Feb 29 2024 19:49:05 GMT+0000 (Coordinated Universal Time)"},{"$kind":"TitledParagraph","text":"Details button to help troubleshooting\nBugfixes and improvements","style":"detail","wantsCollapsedNewlines":true,"primarySubtitle":"1.11.0","secondarySubtitle":"Tue May 30 2023 19:42:48 GMT+0000 (Coordinated Universal Time)"},{"$kind":"TitledParagraph","text":"- support more languages\n- fix connection for UDP protocol","style":"detail","wantsCollapsedNewlines":true,"primarySubtitle":"1.10.0","secondarySubtitle":"Fri Mar 03 2023 07:16:01 GMT+0000 (Coordinated Universal Time)"},{"$kind":"TitledParagraph","text":"Prefix support!","style":"detail","wantsCollapsedNewlines":true,"primarySubtitle":"1.9.0","secondarySubtitle":"Tue Jan 03 2023 17:12:50 GMT+0000 (Coordinated Universal Time)"},{"$kind":"TitledParagraph","text":"- add online config support\n- bug fixes","style":"detail","wantsCollapsedNewlines":true,"primarySubtitle":"1.8.1","secondarySubtitle":"Mon Nov 21 2022 16:07:08 GMT+0000 (Coordinated Universal Time)"},{"$kind":"TitledParagraph","text":"Bug fixes and improvements","style":"detail","wantsCollapsedNewlines":true,"primarySubtitle":"1.8.0","secondarySubtitle":"Thu Oct 13 2022 19:05:06 GMT+0000 (Coordinated Universal Time)"},{"$kind":"TitledParagraph","text":"Bug fixes","style":"detail","wantsCollapsedNewlines":true,"primarySubtitle":"1.7.3","secondarySubtitle":"Fri Oct 07 2022 15:09:39 GMT+0000 (Coordinated Universal Time)"},{"$kind":"TitledParagraph","text":"Bug fixes and improvements!","style":"detail","wantsCollapsedNewlines":true,"primarySubtitle":"1.7.1","secondarySubtitle":"Fri Jul 22 2022 17:08:29 GMT+0000 (Coordinated Universal Time)"},{"$kind":"TitledParagraph","text":"- Update logos and branding.\n- Add Khmer and Burmese translations.\n- Don't collect device timezone and memory stats on crash reports.","style":"detail","wantsCollapsedNewlines":true,"primarySubtitle":"1.5.0","secondarySubtitle":"Thu Jul 01 2021 22:49:59 GMT+0000 (Coordinated Universal Time)"},{"$kind":"TitledParagraph","text":"- Error messaging for unsupported ciphers \n- Reduce server card size when there are multiple servers\n- Add language selection screen \n- Network stability improvements\n- Fix app version not displaying","style":"detail","wantsCollapsedNewlines":true,"primarySubtitle":"1.4.0","secondarySubtitle":"Thu Jul 30 2020 22:19:08 GMT+0000 (Coordinated Universal Time)"},{"$kind":"TitledParagraph","text":"- Updated App Store description.","style":"detail","wantsCollapsedNewlines":true,"primarySubtitle":"1.3.2","secondarySubtitle":"Tue Oct 08 2019 15:19:15 GMT+0000 (Coordinated Universal Time)"},{"$kind":"TitledParagraph","text":"- Update to shadowsocks-libev v3.3.0\n- Localize the app to Khmer\n- Update to Cordova 9\n- Display the port of each server\n- Selection styling to server IP address","style":"detail","wantsCollapsedNewlines":true,"primarySubtitle":"1.3.1","secondarySubtitle":"Mon Aug 26 2019 22:14:41 GMT+0000 (Coordinated Universal Time)"},{"$kind":"TitledParagraph","text":"- Network stack improvements.\n- Improved network change detection robustness.\n- Support pass